OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774991532
OL,3,CUS Army investigating military
OL,4,Chelicopters hovering near Kid Rock's
OL,5,Cmansion
OL,7,FThe US Army say they have launched a
OL,8,Freview after musician Kid Rock shared
OL,9,Fvideos of two military helicopters
OL,10,Fhovering near his Tennessee hillside
OL,11,Fhome over the weekend.
OL,13,FIn the videos, posted to social media,
OL,14,FKid Rock is seen standing by a
OL,15,Fswimming pool, clapping, saluting, and
OL,16,Fraising his fist in the air towards
OL,17,Fthe helicopters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
