PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774991532
OL,3,CUS Army investigating military
OL,4,Chelicopters hovering near Kid Rock's
OL,5,Cmansion
OL,7,F"This is a level of respect the
OL,8,FGovernor of California will never
OL,9,Fknow," Kid Rock wrote, adding: "God
OL,10,FBless America and all those who have
OL,11,Fmade the ultimate sacrifice to defend
OL,12,Fher".
OL,14,FAn outspoken supporter of President
OL,15,FDonald Trump, California Governor
OL,16,FGavin Newsom is a Democrat who has
OL,17,Frepeatedly feuded with Republican
OL,18,FPresident Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
