PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774991532
OL,3,CUS Army investigating military
OL,4,Chelicopters hovering near Kid Rock's
OL,5,Cmansion
OL,7,FThe Army said the AH-64 Apache
OL,8,Fhelicopters were conducting a training
OL,9,Fexercise in the Nashville area, where
OL,10,FKid Rock is believed to live.
OL,12,FThere was no official request to the
OL,13,FArmy from Kid Rock for the helicopters
OL,14,Fto come to his house on Saturday,
OL,15,FMajor Jonathon Bless, public affairs
OL,16,Fofficer for the 101st Airborne
OL,17,FDivision, said on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
