OL,3,CUS Army investigating military
OL,4,Chelicopters hovering near Kid Rock's
OL,5,Cmansion
OL,7,F"An administrative review is underway
OL,8,Fto assess the mission and verify
OL,9,Fcompliance with regulations and
OL,10,Fairspace requirements. Appropriate
OL,11,Faction will be taken if any violations
OL,12,Fare found."
OL,14,FThe helicopters also flew over a
OL,15,FNashville "No Kings" protest against
OL,16,Fthe Trump administration on Saturday,
OL,17,Fbut Bless said the training run had
OL,18,Fnothing to do with the protest.
