OL,7,FThe 101st Airborne Division is located
OL,8,Fat nearby Fort Campbell, on the
OL,9,FTennessee-Kentucky border, and its
OL,10,Fhelicopters often make training runs
OL,11,Fover the Nashville area.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
